  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThe validator client currently has a --reuse-password flag that allows it to reuse the same password when importing keys. However, it does NOT have this feature during normal operation when decrypting keys that don't have a password stored in validator_definitions.yml. Without this feature, running multiple validators without the password stored is way too tedious.",
